ign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Hunting at 12 Solo</span><hr size=1> Well I attempted grouping in NRO and dinged 12....got my new pet...and I dont know if it is just me but I LOVE getting a new pet.  I finally got burn out and I don't know if it much difference....<br>
<br>
Well my question is where could I go to hunt solo at level 12 with my new pet?  I would hunt nro but the scarabs and spiders are low blue and green now....madmen and mummies are now rare to find even thought they always found me before...kinda odd how that works..<br>
<br>
any suggestions will help greatly. <p><img src="http://www.mronderko.com/zek.gif">
