<br>
Drakes will be even to blue to you.  Good exp, and easy kills.  I hit them with one shock of blades pulled to put, and cast rain of blades.  Medded up, while pet killed htem and then repeated. Had very little down time.<br>
<br>
Just remember NO fire damage will stick here.  I used my water pet and blade spells.  Don't bother with your fire lines, or with your pet's DS, it wn't do a thing. <br>
<br>
